A 99-year-old woman was killed in Shakaskraal near KwaDukuza, north of Durban on Friday, paramedic services said. According to IPSS spokesperson Dylan Meyrick, the woman and a 3-year-old were struck by the truck."The woman was dragged under the truck wheels and suffered massive inquiries. Despite efforts by advanced life support paramedics she was declared on scene."Meyrick said advanced life support paramedics were currently treating the critically injured child.News24 Source http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/99-year-old-dragged-killed-by-truck-20170825